{"tid":192170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習特會】Trump唔戴耳筒 專登唔聽習總講嘢？","createTime":"2017-04-08T11:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T13:01:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6deff16ba599d3aae722433f43242f3547b73dbf","tid":192170,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:34:51.000Z","msg":"特朗普與習近平舉行會談，很多小動作都顯示他的內心如何看待習總。繼早前被拍到在晚宴上，特朗普與習總握手時，手在下面、表情微妙後，他又被媒體發現在會談期間，習總發言之時，特朗普沒有戴上耳筒聽即時傳譯，疑是根本沒聽習的發言。<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮上傳的影片顯示，中美元首會面時，習近平在發表開場講話，特朗普旁邊的官員全都戴上耳筒，聽即時傳譯的內容，唯獨特朗普一人沒有戴上。當習近平音語音一落，特朗普便以感謝習近平到美國接上。<br />\n除此以外，當地時間6日晚上特朗普與習近平晚宴時，特朗普在鏡頭前除歡迎習近平及彭麗媛到訪，但他之後卻說：「我們討論了很長時間但是我什麼也沒有得到，絕對沒有！」（We had a long discussion already and so far I have gotten nothing, absolutely nothing.）<br />\nYouTube  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56536772&amp;category_guid=9999803&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56536772%26category_guid%3D9999803%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170408&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8d5aeb70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56536772%26category_guid%3D9999803%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170408&h=75f4d07d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56536772&amp;category_guid=9999803&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170408</a>"},{"pid":"3e27d4611651dc2d2a9260e0aaa2c1436ef79adb","tid":192170,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"使鬼聽咩，又咪係嗰啲「建立新型大國關係」啊、「支國從來不稱霸」啊之類嘅陳腔濫調，唔通會講「我想入籍美國，幾時批張綠卡俾我？」咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f988a36ab9894081d3ad213992ffb5e863ebf30","tid":192170,"uid":65847,"like":0,"d